.SH Version 19.5.1 (2013\-12\-02)
.PP
This release restores support for Capybara integration tests in the \fB\fCrails\fR
configuration helper, corrects the \fB\fCidle\fR event in 
.BR tork-engine (1), 
and fixes
some minor bugs in 
.BR tork-runner (1) 
and 
.BR tork (1).
.SS Patch:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Rails: keep sub\-Rails connected to in\-memory SQLite3 test database.
.PP
When another Rails instance is started by Capybara, it sets up a new
connection to the test database instead of re\-using our in\-memory DB.
.TP
\[la]http://www.spacevatican.org/2012/8/18/threading-the-rat/\[ra]
.IP \(bu 2
.BR tork-engine (1) 
sent \fB\fCidle\fR event when 1 test was still running.
.IP \(bu 2
