.RS
.IP \(bu 2
You must now explicitly \fB\fCrequire 'test/loop/rails'\fR for Rails support
because we can only \fIautomatically\fP apply our Railtie (to disable class
caching) after the overhead has been loaded, and by then it's too late:
your models are already loaded & cached by the Rails environment.
.IP \(bu 2
